<F P=102>  PA2101141094 Mexico City XEW Television Network in Spanish 
0443 GMT 21 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA2101141094 </F>
<F P=104>  Mexico City XEW Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Bulletin No. 24 issued by the Mexican National Defense </F>
Secretariat in Mexico City on 20 January; from the "24 Hours" 
newscast] 
  [Text] (Isabel Maria Rabel), a Swiss national assigned to 
the UN High Commissioner for Refugees, and William Calderon 
Sanchez, a Mexican national, arrived at a military checkpoint in 
Chancala at 1545 [2145 GMT] aboard a Wagoneer-type vehicle 
registered as OZFDSRORG INT MEX, belonging to the United 
Nations. They stated that at 1200 [1800 GMT] 20 armed men 
carrying rifles and hand grenades held them up near the 200 km 
marker along the Palenque Benemerito de las Americas Highway. 
The men wore gray shirts and dark trousers and had their faces 
covered. They robbed Calderon Sanchez of 1,000 new pesos and 
his credit and identification cards. 

</TEXT>

