<H3> <TI>   Congress Approves Chiapas Presidential Amnesty </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  PA2201043794 Mexico City Radio ACIR Network in Spanish 0030 
GMT 22 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> PA2201043794 </F>
<F P=104>  Mexico City Radio ACIR Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "Vector 21" newscast] </F>
  [Text] Here in Mexico City, the Senate approved the 
presidential amnesty initiative for Chiapas State, with the 
opposition of PRD [Party of the Democratic Revolution] 
