<F P=101> Haiti </F>
<H3> <TI>   CNRCH To Demonstrate for Lifting of Sanctions </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  FL2101231894 Port-au-Prince Radio Metropole in French 1400 
GMT 21 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> FL2101231894 </F>
<F P=104>  Port-au-Prince Radio Metropole </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> French </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A demonstration is scheduled for 21 January in 
Port-au-Prince. The National Committee for the Resolution of the 
Haitian Crisis [Comite National de Resolution de la Crise 
Haitienne, CNRCH] will stage this demonstration supporting the 
immediate establishment of a responsible government and the 
immediate and unconditional lifting of UN and OAS sanctions as 
well as the lifting of the embargo. Those organizing this 
demonstration hope to gather several dozens of thousands of 
people. 

</TEXT>

