<F P=103> PA2501133994 </F>
<F P=104>  Caracas Venezolana de Television Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Spanish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From "The News" newscast] </F>
  [Text] Labor Minister Luis Horacio Vivas Pena announced 
the opening of the National Occupational Welfare, Health, and 
Safety Institute [Instituto Nacional de Prevision, Salud, y 
